Sweeping up her normally long, golden tresses under what looked like a short, brunette wig, Aniston was spotted on set rocking a shoulder-grazing bob with bangs that did little to flatter her pretty face. She donned the shaggy look while filming scenes for her movie "Squirrels to the Nuts" in New York City on July 17, 2013.
